	Cookies:
		small piece of data that server sends to client
		client(Browser) store them  and automatically sends with every request to same domain'
		
		steps to work with cookie	
		
		1. install cookie-parser
		
		2. set middleware
			app.use(cookieParser());
			
		3. set cookies
			
			res.cookie('key':'value',{
				maxAge:1000*60,
				httpOnly:true,
			})
			
		4. get cookies
			req.cookies
			
		5. res.clearCookie('key')
		
		